title: Larry Webster (HAGERTY)
description: This week Larry Webster of Hagerty joins us to talk Pebble Beach, racing and 911s.  Larry starts off with tails of an E46 procrastination special, shares his story of moving from engineering to journalism and recounts a fairly epic day on Tail of the Dragon.  Additionally Matt is seriously considering selling the DeLorean and we talk about the Exocet Miata conversion.
author: matt@thesmokingtire.com (Matt Farah & Zack Klapman)
